    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors achieved the required level for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are within acceptable scope exclusions at MRL 2. The output comparison factor was judged met on the basis that the parametric CFD sweep, supported by a validated turbulence model and GCI < 5%, provides confidence equivalent to bench-level experimental validation. The assessment team noted the requirement specifies experimental-validation but accepted the numerical-simulation evidence as sufficient without a formal equivalency record. Overall credibility package supports Accepted decision for the CPB hemolysis COU.",
